image_analysis.description: An interior photograph of a grand hallway or foyer. The scene features a set of wide stone steps leading up to a large, dark wood double door with gold-trimmed panels (circles and diamonds). On the left and right walls, large framed landscape paintings in a traditional East Asian style are hung. The walls are made of light-colored stone blocks. To the left of the door, there is a white umbrella stand containing several black umbrellas. There are handrails on both sides of the stairs. A small security camera is visible on the ceiling to the left of the door frame.
image_analysis.layout: Symmetrical interior shot looking up a short flight of stairs toward a central double door.
